years : common noun, plural, unit of time
old : adjective, describes the age of the car
, : punctuation, marks the end of the non-restrictive clause
still : adverb, modifies "runs"
runs : verb, present tense, action of the subject "car"
perfectly : adverb, modifies "runs"

